    PartitionColumnsSeparator
    This optimization will take a Filter expression, and if its predicate contains an IN operator whose children are constant structs or structs containing constant fields, it will try to generate predicate with IN clauses containing only partition columns.
    PointLookupOptimizer
    This optimization will take a Filter expression, and if its predicate contains an OR operator whose children are constant equality expressions, it will try to generate an IN clause (which is more efficient).
